-shooting-christmas-market-13720650&d=yUURsNYXfk%2Fv0Fz7DWYp2mi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=625664fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/breaking-strasbourg-shooting-christmas-market-13720650</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/@48.5823786,7.7474975,3a,60y,233.24h,90t/data=!3m6!1e1!3m4!1se6_KRk0fOUizibmTsBBbYQ!2e0!7i13312!8i6656\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2F%4048.5823786%2C7.7474975%2C3a%2C60y%2C233.24h%2C90t%2Fdata%3D%213m6%211e1%213m4%211se6_KRk0fOUizibmTsBBbYQ%212e0%217i13312%218i6656&d=yUURsNYXfk%2Fv0Fz7DWYp2mi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=2b6d7e86\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/@48.5823786,7.7474975,3a,60y,233.24h,90t/data=!3m6!1e1!3m4!1se6_KRk0fOUizibmTsBBbYQ!2e0!7i13312!8i6656</a>"},{"pid":"b6231912cb1bc47e7993887b47bbcc32212da4b7","tid":937793,"uid":34119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T21:33:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.sky.com/story/one-dead-in-french-christmas-market-shooting-11578206\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fone-dead-in-french-christmas-market-shooting-11578206&d=yUURsNYXfk%2Fv0Fz7DWYp2mi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=c2850479\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.sky.com/story/one-dead-in-french-christmas-market-shooting-11578206</a>"},{"pid":"7830c025fafb34e2fa4ac02a0dec313add641cd9","tid":937793,"uid":34119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T21:35:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/斯特拉斯堡\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%96%AF%E7%89%B9%E6%8B%89%E6%96%AF%E5%A0%A1&d=yUURsNYXfk%2Fv0Fz7DWYp2mi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=3587fb1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/斯特拉斯堡</a><br />\n史特拉斯堡也是眾多國際組織總部所在地的城市。史特拉斯堡與比利時的首都布魯塞爾一樣，<strong>駐有歐盟的許多重要機構，包括歐洲委員會</strong>、歐洲人權法院、歐盟反貪局、歐洲軍團、歐洲視聽觀察，以及<strong>歐洲議會</strong>的所在地，因此<strong>被譽為歐盟的「第二首都」</strong>。史特拉斯堡是歐洲議會的所在地，儘管每個月只在史特拉斯堡舉行四天會議，其他主要事務則在布魯塞爾處理。議會大廈建於1998年，是世界上最大的議會建築。"},{"pid":"ad414a9c398b477208ac8bde326031fda15a0289","tid":937793,"uid":34119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T21:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509114b111abaedcc4be41afa6da371d2b31eb46","tid":937793,"uid":34119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T22:15:20.000Z","msg":"依加四死七傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbe3da37c0f1e955d02750d1ef6012e238c5502","tid":937793,"uid":34119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T22:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />mx"},{"pid":"a625b8609e06add88af1ef419ac2b9c3a19be593","tid":937793,"uid":34119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T22:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181212/large/1544558540_a3e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181212%2Flarge%2F1544558540_a3e3.jpg&h=168709b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181212/59019977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F59019977&d=yUURsNYXfk%2Fv0Fz7DWYp2mi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=878f864c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F59019977&h=410f8438\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181212/59019977</a><br />\n法國東北部斯特拉斯堡（Strasbourg）市中心一個聖誕市集周二晚發生槍擊案，警方指造成4死多人重傷，多名傷者危殆。槍手在逃，但已被警員包圍。檢察官已將案件列作恐怖襲擊調查。<br />\n警方表示曾與槍手駁火，指槍手較早時在市集附近被士兵槍傷。<br />\n有商店東主表示，槍擊持續10分鐘，人群爭相走避。網上流傳有人倒地或走避的片段。<br />\n槍擊發生後，大批荷槍實彈警員到場，疏散克勒貝爾廣場（Place Kleber）及附近食肆的人。內政部指發生了嚴重保安事件，呼籲案發現場一帶公眾留在室內。<br />\n警方指槍手是29歲劫匪，因涉及早前一宗企圖謀殺，警方準備周二早上拘捕他。警方又指槍手曾涉犯罪活動，被情報當局列為涉嫌極端分子。<br />\n歐洲議會總部位於斯特拉斯堡，發言人表示大樓亦被封鎖。<br />\n總統府發言人表示，總統馬克龍暫停會議，留意事態發展，並派內政部長卡斯塔內（Christophe Castaner）到斯特拉斯堡了解事件。<br />\n事發地點在斯特拉斯堡的聖誕市集。該市集每年吸引數以百萬計遊客。"},{"pid":"a8e6ab023d62d303c8d4ff923911db0da054e324","tid":937793,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T23:30:33.000Z","msg":"歐洲就理9得佢死啦  左膠自己攞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5e5558216faffa075a6ce5f66f345589f3e3c9","tid":937793,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T00:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821baa9a36fbe401c5c29264bd1632c2306ce908","tid":937793,"uid":64191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T00:42:54.000Z","msg":"槍手好似係摩洛哥裔，但曾經因爲支持ISIS而列入監管名單"}]}